template.name: Template - Check my Website
template.description: Collects monitoring information from the web site https://checkmy.ws

item.name: Expiration date of the domain name
item.description: Returns the date when the domain name for the monitored URL expires.

item.name: Availability over 24h
item.description: Returns the percentage of availability for the URL over the last 24h.

item.name: Number of Javascript errors
item.description: Returns the number of Javascript errors raised by a browser when browsing the URL.

item.name: Number of objects not found
item.description: Returns the number of requests fired from the URL ending in a 40X HTTP code.

item.name: Number of redirects
item.description: Returns the number of requests fired from the URL ending in a 30X HTTP code.

item.name: Number of requests
item.description: Total number of HTTP requests fired from the URL.

item.name: Availability test result
item.description: Returns the description of the availability test result.

item.name: Availability test result (code)
item.description: Availability test result in the number form.

item.name: Yslow score
item.description: Score given by the performance analyzer Yslow.

item.name: Total size of other elements
item.description: Total size of elements other than CSS, JavaScript, image, document or font downloaded from the URL.

item.name: Total size of stylesheet data
item.description: Total size of CSS data downloaded from the URL.

item.name: Total size of image data
item.description: Total size of image data downloaded from the URL.

item.name: Total size of font data
item.description: Total size of web font data downloaded from the URL.

item.name: Total size of Javascript data
item.description: Total size of Javascript data downloaded from the URL.

item.name: Total size of document data
item.description: Total size of HTML (document) data downloaded from the URL.

item.name: Total size
item.description: Total size of all data downloaded from the URL.

item.name: Total loading time (Yslow)
item.description: Time the URL and its linked elements took to load from a browser point of view.

item.name: State
item.description: Global state of the URL as a number. 0 means OK.

discovery_rule.name: Locations
discovery_rule.description: List of the monitoring locations configured in the https://checkmy.ws interface.

trigger_prototype.name: Check my Website reported an outage on {HOST.NAME} from {#LOCATION_CITY} ({#LOCATION_COUNTRY}, {#LOCATION_ISP})
trigger_prototype.description: One availability probe is non zero.

trigger.name: Check my Website reported an outage on {HOST.NAME}
trigger.description: The URL is not available according to https://checkmy.ws
